com.satori.rtm.model

Class SubscriptionInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.satori.rtm.model.SubscriptionInfo

  • public class SubscriptionInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the body value of a PDU for a subscription info. SubscriptionInfo objects provide information about a subscription, including the type of info and the reason why RTM sent the info.

    RTM doesn't terminate your subscription after it sends a subscription info.
